{"tid":337300,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［五毛有工開］ 俄亥俄機動遊戲故障　多人半空拋出　1死7傷","createTime":"2017-07-27T07:47:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-27T08:03:14.000Z","uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f964677e41b9848f62640ce298a7b23bd276c358","tid":337300,"uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T07:47:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170727/s00005/1501129923237\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170727%2Fs00005%2F1501129923237&d=ELUN%2FiwwjC2LvQyS5Q5eCEkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=e6240b4a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170727%2Fs00005%2F1501129923237&h=14a9578b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170727/s00005/1501129923237</a><br />\n<br />\n美國俄亥俄州一個嘉年華發生致命機動遊戲意外，在遊戲機運作期間，其中一節座位飛脫，多人在空中被拋出，造成一名男子死亡，至少7人受傷，當中3人危殆。當局稱事前安全檢查並無異樣，已勒令關閉嘉年華所有機動遊戲，直至完成安全檢查。<br />\n<br />\n事發於當時周三（26日）嘉年華開幕當晚，有人拍攝到機動遊戲「火球（fireball）」故障一刻。從片段所見，每卡座位由吊臂連接到機動遊戲的主吊臂，當吊臂擺動期間，其中一卡座位脫離機身，多人被拋出空中。事件造成一名男子當場死亡，至少7人受傷，當中3人危殆，其中一名傷者是13歲的女童。<br />\n<br />\n有正在排隊玩「火球」的目擊者指，至少兩人被拋到空中，離地至少6米後墮地，當局指，該機動遊戲已通過安全檢查。俄亥俄州州長卡西奇（Kasich）形容事件是非常可怕的悲劇，承諾會徹查事件。<br />\n<br />\n嘉年華原定舉行至8月6日，當局下令關閉嘉年華內所有機動遊戲，直至完成額外的安全檢查。<br />\n<br />\n（CNN／每日郵報）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170727/s00005/1501129923237\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170727%2Fs00005%2F1501129923237&d=ELUN%2FiwwjC2LvQyS5Q5eCEkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=e6240b4a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170727%2Fs00005%2F1501129923237&h=14a9578b\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170727/s00005/1501129923237</a>"},{"pid":"6b17968b26fc061761f6e6d62b5b27d39a5b56a4","tid":337300,"uid":25556,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T07:49:10.000Z","msg":"又係支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82232a504f9b7d2502d16b08d838bbb1be583bc1","tid":337300,"uid":29609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T07:57:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又係支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n黑人問號.jpg"},{"pid":"70bc775645ee038618d29737389bb6aa308bff9b","tid":337300,"uid":6968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T08:03:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>又係支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n黑人問號.jpg</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nr撚哂頭"}]}